      • get

        MapArray<String,MapArray<String,ICell>> get()
        Description copied from interface: ITableLine
        Get Columns/Rows in following format
        For rows: rowName>columnName>cell
        For columns: columnName>rowName>cell
        e.g. myTable.columns().get().get("Name").get("5") or myTable.columns().get().count() But better to use specified commands like cell("Name, "5") myTable.columns().count()

        get in interface ITableLine
